fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the resource. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: RegistrationEnabled
fields.description: Is auto-registration of virtual machine records in the virtual network in the Private DNS zone enabled?

fields.name: VirtualNetwork
fields.description: The reference of the virtual network.

fields.name: VirtualNetworkLinkState
fields.description: The status of the virtual network link to the Private DNS zone. Possible values are 'InProgress' and 'Done'. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.
